{"about_the_game":"Deckarium is a deck-building pet simulator. Play pet cards to add to your terrarium or aquarium, and progress through levels to unlock new cards to add to your deck.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/frog.gif?t=1736984387\" /><br><br>Keep your pets well fed and they'll produce coins for you. Some pets have bigger appetites than others! You will have to maintain the food-chain if you want to benefit from larger pets.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/foodchain.gif?t=1736984387\" /><br><br>Your pets aren't the only ones who are hungry! Beware of ghosts who seek only to consume the souls of your pets!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/ghost.gif?t=1736984387\" /><br><br>Beat levels and minigames to earn extra currency for your own personal idle terrarium and aquarium, where you can collect and name your own unique pets without fear of phantoms!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011230/extras/snail.gif?t=1736984387\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beginner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3011230/f0fe8e3c157c7f304f96fd913403182e27bffb6e.jpg"},{"name":"Endurance","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3011230/6be59a1b529cb74a7b0800a9cc25b884c867cef4.jpg"},{"name":"Finish","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3011230/c90ca03e33126866487bb6830d762d105c70c6fb.jpg"},{"name":"Endless","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3011230/dbb6213ef9fdcd4cb9d1786ce38ecc3263a6e109.jpg"},{"name":"Minigame expert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/ap